\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 19\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Though I am free\'a0and belong to no one, I have made myself a slave to everyone,\'a0to win as many as possible.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub To the Jews I became like a Jew, to win the Jews.\'a0To those under the law I became like one under the law (though I myself am not under the law),\'a0so as to win those under the law.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 21\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub To those not having the law I became like one not having the law\'a0(though I am not free from God\'92s law but am under Christ\'92s law),\'a0so as to win those not having the law.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 22\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub To the weak I became weak, to win the weak.\'a0I have become all things to all people\'a0so that by all possible means I might save some.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 23\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I do all this for the sake of the gospel, that I may share in its blessings.  1 Cor 9\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He will do anything (that is what by ALL means means) short of sin to reach people for Jesus\'85and this is our grid.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We will do anything short of sin to reach those who are far from God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What if something is offensive to people\'85That isn\'92t the grid we will be using!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You know why?  Because Jesus wasn\'92t concerned about that at all!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 I had an idea the other day where some of the people on the team were a little appalled is probably the right word\'85and my question was simple\'85who would it offend?  The religious people in the community or non-Christian people we say we are trying to reach?  Too often we held captive by people we are not called to reach or impact.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
