\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 13\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub He replied,\'a0\'93Every plant that my heavenly Father has not planted\'a0will be pulled up by the roots.
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 14\'a0
