\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Mark 5 - Killed Pigs \'96 PETA would hate him\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Matthew 11 - Killed a tree because he got mad it \'96 Environmentalist who worship the earth wouldn\'92t like that\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Luke 141 - Told people to hate their parents \'96 Focus on the Family couldn\'92t stand that guy\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In Mark 6 he called a bunch of modern day pastors names and was incredibly intolerant of them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Mark 1 \'96 Told strangers they were going to hell.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}John 6 - He was incredibly confusing and offensive when He told a crowd to eat his flesh and drink his blood.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Luke 22  \'96 Jesus tells people swords are more important than clothes.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
